==Microphone placement== 
'''Each technique begins with a bullet point.'''

*Place an [[XY stereo microphone technique|X/Y]] small diaphragm condenser pair roughly 3 feet away from the center of the dulcimer 
*Place a [[AB_stereo_mic_technique|spaced pair]] of [[omnidirectional]] microphones about 1-2 feet apart and about 2-3 feet above the instrument 


